															  <font class="blocktext">We will work with you to determine the exact requirements for your software. RMT2 Business Systems Corp will observe how you do your work, so we can make sure that we understand what you want. If you have already started to document what you want the software to do, we will use that material and move forward on the project from your preliminary work.</font>
